Author: LolitaJane
Text: If you didn't have an eating disorder, you wouldn't be this fixated on it.  EDs happen in the mind, and their effects on the body are side-effects of a mental illness.

Author: TheManyArchetypes
Text: You keep posting here and fat logic and you are being told that you are not seeing things clearly. You clearly have a problem, congratulations.  You have claimed a bmi around 21-22. You are not fat. You have posted selfies saying you are fat when you clearly are not. You are not disgusting.    Your attitude in comments is prerry disgusting though, and you need to start being more mindful about how you communicate on an eating dissorder sub.  I'm seriously starting to suspect you are actually a troll.
